data.description: INVESTORS SPECIAL! This home has many possibilities. Two lots allow for the opportunity for a great outdoor area. Just minutes away from Lake Whitney, considered one of the prettiest lakes in Texas with top notch stiped bass fishing and many options for public access. Lake Whitney is a popular destination for family and fishermen alike! This property has great potential to be income producing or updated for a quint personal home close to the water! Agents please see private remarks or call listing agent for more information.  This property is AS-IS.  Roof replaced in 2018.
